node.title: Motorcyclist dies in crash in rural Waikato
node.description: A man has died in a single motorcycle crash in Rangiriri north of Huntly earlier today.
node.content:
["A man has died in a single motorcycle crash in Rangiriri north of Huntly earlier today.", "", "
\nPhoto: RNZ / Tom Kitchin\n
", "Emergency services were called to the crash site on Whangamarino Road shortly before 1pm, but the motorcyclist died at the scene.", "The serious crash unit is also at the scene and the road remains closed while their investigations are underway.", "Motorists are advised to avoid the area and choose an alternate route."]
